#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:40
#: c612e4c374284ba4a4c261a637095e87
msgid ""
"At each iteration :math:`k`, every inactive node :math:`i` checks the "
"fraction (or weighted fraction) of its neighbors that are active. If this "
"value exceeds its threshold :math:`\\theta_i`, the node becomes active in "
"the next iteration."
msgstr ""
"在每次迭代:`k'时,每个不活动节点:`i ' 检查其邻国活跃的分数(或加权分数)。 如果该值超过其阈值 : math: QXTHETA i "
",则节点在下一个迭代中开始活动 。"

