#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:48
#: a9510ab3b2fa4088b3b62b78dd9398da
msgid ""
"We use one Boolean indicator vector :math:`h \\in \\{0,1\\}^N`, where "
":math:`h_i=1` denotes ``Active``, :math:`h_i=0` denotes ``Inactive``."
msgstr ""
"我们使用一个布尔指标矢量:math:`h\\ in \\{0,1\\}^N',其中:math:`h i=1'表示`积极',`math:`h "
"i=0'表示`不积极'。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:50
#: 84f57630ee4640648ba998ee9e121b09
msgid ""
"Each active neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a contribution"
msgstr "每个活跃的邻居:math:节点的`j':math:`i'传递一份贡献."

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:52
#: 9ac224cc8a984cf4b97d36d061357682
msgid ""
"m_{ji}^{(k)} = h_j^{(k-1)}\n"
"\n"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)} = h j^{(k-1)] (中文(简体) )."

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:55
#: 4cd3a870cca24272a1de73654d9c068a
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its active probability:"
msgstr "节点:math:`i'收集来自所有邻居的捐款:math:`N(i)'计算其活动概率:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:57
#: 2aaab66379634980afa3a4124e47c12e
msgid ""
"m_i^{(k)} = \\frac{1}{|N(i)|}\\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"==============================================================================================================================================================================================================================================================="

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:60
#: 10f08e4142c64cef91abeb0d7b23c9e1
msgid "The indicator variables are updated by:"
msgstr "指标变量通过以下方式更新:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/Threshold.rst:62
#: 21ef1805be274a15afaa31006356dd2d
msgid ""
" h_i^{(k)} =\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    1,  \\text{if} (\\theta_i \\leq m_i^{(k)}) \\land h_i^{(k-1)}=0 , \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    h_i^{(k-1)},  \\text{otherwise},\n"
"\\end{cases} \\\\[6pt]"
msgstr ""
"h i^{(k)}=\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1,\\text{if} (\\theta i\\leq m i^{(k)})\\land h i^{(k-1)\\0,\\\\[4pt]\n"
"h i^{(k-1)},\\text{另类},\n"
"\\ end{ cases}\\\\\\ [6pt]"

